The Korean National Chemicals Information System (NCiS) can be used to search for GHS Classifications for chemicals. GreenScreen List Translator only includes chemicals in 5 broad search categories: Phase-in substances subject to registration, Toxic Substances, Restricted Substances, Prohibited Substances, and Substances requiring preparation for accidents.
